Internet booster improves the coverage and provides a stable signal for you. Creating a stable high-speed network environment for transfer large digital files, videos and online games.（NOTE : All Wi-Fi extenders are designed to increase or improve Wi-Fi coverage, not to directly increase speed.)

WPS One-Tap Setup & 3 In 1 Functions: It can easily extend the wireless coverage by pressing the WPS button only takes 8 seconds to connect to your device.Repeater Mode is for extending Wi-Fi coverage of an existing wireless network. AP Mode is for covering a wired network to a wireless network. The two Ethernet ports being able to connect to any wired ethernet device such as smart TV, desktop,etc.

Stable 360°Full Coverage : This Wi-Fi booster covers up to 9800 sq.ft, with 4 External High-Gain Antennas will provide a more stable signal and greater penetration to beat frustrating Wi-Fi dead zones with superior performance.Signal amplifier can penetrate obstacles such as floors and concrete walls, and provide you with a stable Wi-Fi signal indoors, you can enjoy online games, video conferences and even play 4K high-definition video anytime and anywhere at home.

Wi-Fi Signal Security Protocol : You can find the best placement of the Wi-Fi repeater according to the change of the signal indicator.Three lights means strong signal. Two lights means general signal. (Too far away from the main router.) One light means weak signal. (Please move it closer to the router or reset the extender). This internet Wi-Fi extender can maximize the network security, ensure your network safety, avoid the interference and privacy problems of Wi-Fi.

Wide Compatibility With Over 45 Devices : This signal amplifier complies with the IEEE 802.11a/b/g/n,802.11ac standard protocol and is compatible with most of wireless network devices, routers and Wi-Fi devicescan easily connect to most brands of router and access point and support over 45 devices such as smartphone, PC, laptop, smart TV,online gaming and whatever standard Wi-Fi routers and Wi-Fi enabled devices.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This extender is absolutely fabulous
reviews.reviewText: It replaced one that was giving me uploads of 18 and downloads of 3. This one gives me the same value that got when in the room with the modem. Those numbers were 56 Mbps upload and 59 Mbps download. It also show signal strength of where you plug it in. This can help you find the best spot.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to use, effective, and fast
reviews.reviewText: I bought this device because I wanted to create an access point for Wi-Fi devices in the corner of my house furthest away from my main router. I have this device connected to my router by ethernet cable, and this broadcasts a second Wi-Fi signal that works whenever I am out of the range of my primary router. This was the perfect solution and a great price. I am pleased.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Weak security trumps excellent set up, speed and range extension
reviews.reviewText: Returning this despite the product doing everything as described, because of something that isn’t addressed: its weak security. It’s a dealbreaker to have a powerful extender share data with anyone in the vicinity of my house because of weak security. This is the question I posted that was answered by the seller:Q: The 2.4 and 5G networks both have "weak security" messages in AP and Repeater modes. My router is at WPA2 AES. How do I strengthen the security?A: You can use this wifi repeater for itYou plug this and connect your router thought this repeater using the same passwordBy Winter Seller Hub in the United States on February 8, 2024I purchased another repeater/access point at the same time as this one and it doesn’t produce the “weak security” message when connecting to its 2.4 or 5 GHz. This one goes back to Amazon so I can purchase the other one - too bad because this router is otherwise excellent. Buy it if you think a great passcode is enough to secure your network, but do your homework if you want to avoid the possible hassle of identity theft.
